{"tid":2327325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍緯汶非禮兩名少數族裔女童囚32個月 官斥「心目中冇愛只有性」","createTime":"2020-12-16T03:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T06:30:11.000Z","uid":241764,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b047b61ebaa92cf84c5b2ef3c7f3cce2c841fd87","tid":2327325,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"被告龍緯汶（46歲）早前承認三項向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為、兩項非禮罪、一項製作兒童色情物品及一項管有兒童色情物品罪，案發於2017至2019年間。兩名非華裔事主分別為X及Y，X事發時4至7歲，Y則為3至5歲。龍緯汶今日聽判期間，全程低頭。<br />\n<br />\n法官沈小民判刑時指，對被告揚言待X長大後會與他成為情侶的說法不表接納，認為「聽來已知不合情理」，任何思想正常的成年人，對幼齡女童產生的都應是愛護、而非情侶間的愛意，因年幼女童不可能作出雙向愛意，直指被告明顯是找藉口侵犯女童，「心目中冇愛只有性」，故判刑一定要具阻嚇力。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/MNA3JCB25VAPTLROXMPX2IXSLU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3b3qhXOSkMXigCh3mj_aDlQvge5tKTnT0HYDEfOwRDO6VcPp-cPmnserY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FMNA3JCB25VAPTLROXMPX2IXSLU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3b3qhXOSkMXigCh3mj_aDlQvge5tKTnT0HYDEfOwRDO6VcPp-cPmnserY&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU74BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=fa9214fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FMNA3JCB25VAPTLROXMPX2IXSLU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3b3qhXOSkMXigCh3mj_aDlQvge5tKTnT0HYDEfOwRDO6VcPp-cPmnserY&h=64dd28e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/MNA3JCB25VAPTLROXMPX2IXSLU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3b3qhXOSkMXigCh3mj_aDlQvge5tKTnT0HYDEfOwRDO6VcPp-cPmnserY</a>"},{"pid":"8da60459c8a812d46fadbeb5b05a9f4cce50a1a3","tid":2327325,"uid":157197,"